the application contains multi-center student learning and satisfaction management system. the main goal is to track the student satisfaction level, his attendence, syllabus taught. missed topics. faculty progress, faculty feedback.etc.
master account can add center, each center will have saperate account, center head has all controls, master center can see all center reports.
center head will add student, assign him subjects and faculties.
faculty will mark attendence of student along with topic taught. 
focus only on individual or personal teaching,
faculty can mark student as present, absent, leave, holiday, and completed
complete students are shown in admins login so that he can transfer the student to another faculty.
while marking attencence, facluty will select in time and out time of student also.
faculty can add subject topics also
admin can mark backdated attendence with topics taught, as faculty does
admin can update or send feedback links to students email.
admin can see all reports, overall center report, student reports, and faculty reports. use gantt charts , timelines to see student learning progress
admin can see detailed insights. students absent from last 3 days, extended student. add more insights 